OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright morning with sunny
OL,6,Fintervals and the odd shower. Cloud
OL,7,Fspreads north with rain soon following
OL,8,Fthis afternoon, becoming heavy and
OL,9,Fturning to snow to fairly low levels
OL,10,Fwith heavy falls on high ground.
OL,11,FStrengthening northeasterly winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FFurther rain sleet and snow,
OL,14,Fheavy at times this evening, and
OL,15,Fstrong to gale force northerly winds,
OL,16,Fsevere around coasts. Winds easing and
OL,17,Fturning showery overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
