OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FA bright mainly dry start with
OL,6,Fsunshine and isolated showers. Cloud
OL,7,Fincreasing to bring a band of rain
OL,8,Fsleet or snow around middle of day
OL,9,Fbefore brightening again later.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMostly
OL,12,Fdry on Monday, some sunshine but
OL,13,Fclouding over, patchy rain for Isles.
OL,14,FSunny start Tuesday, then rain
OL,15,Freaching west later, some heavy.
OL,16,FOccasional rain or showers on
OL,17,FWednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
